<body>

<h1>🔍 Spot the Risk</h1>
<p class="subtitle">Six scenarios. Real patterns. Faculty who noticed — and what they did next.</p>

<div class="scenario-nav">
  <button class="nav-btn active" onclick="showCard(0)">1</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showCard(1)">2</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showCard(2)">3</button>
  <button class="nav-btn" onclick="showCard(3)">4</button>
